description: Charming 2-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom detached single-family home located just off of K Street. This cozy residence offers a bright, eat-in kitchen perfect for casual dining and gatherings. The spacious living areas create a welcoming atmosphere, ideal for both relaxation and entertaining. Step outside to enjoy a small patio, offering a private outdoor space for morning coffee or evening relaxation. With plenty of potential and a fantastic location, this home is perfect for those looking to settle into a comfortable, low-maintenance lifestyle. Don't miss out on this wonderful opportunity! Offers due Sunday at 5pm.
